subject: NCAA Wrestling Championships
Wrestling
Colleges and Universities
lead_paragraph: The Cornell senior Kyle Dake became the first wrestler in N.C.A.A. history to win four national titles at four weights, and Penn State won the national championship for the third year in a row.
